### Test Upload, Audit Log, Multiple Answers, Rate Limiting

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7249
@accessToken = PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ===== UPLOAD =====

### 1. Upload image cho câu hỏi (dùng Postman/Thunder Client)
# Multipart form-data với key "file"
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Upload/image?folder=questions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 2. Xóa file đã upload
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Upload?fileUrl=https://localhost:7249/uploads/questions/abc.jpg
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ===== MULTIPLE ANSWERS =====

### 3. Lưu nhiều đáp án cho 1 câu (Multiple correct)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Exam/answer-multiple
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idBaiThi": 1,
  "idCauHoi": 1,
  "idLuaChonDaChon": [1, 3, 4],
  "cauTraLoiTuLuan": null,
  "daLuu": true
}

### ===== AUDIT LOG =====

### 4. Lấy log gần nhất
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/AuditLog/recent?top=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5. Lấy log của 1 user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/AuditLog/user/1?top=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 6. Lấy log của 1 bài thi
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/AuditLog/exam-session/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 7. Tìm kiếm log theo action type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/AuditLog/search?actionType=POST_API_AUTH_LOGIN
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 8. Tìm kiếm log theo thời gian
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/AuditLog/search?from=2026-05-20T00:00:00&to=2026-05-22T00:00:00
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ===== RATE LIMITING =====

### 9. Test rate limit cho login (10 req/phút)
# Spam request này 11 lần liên tục - request thứ 11 sẽ bị 429
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test",
  "password": "wrong",
  "rememberMe": false
}

### ===== HEALTH CHECK =====

### 10. Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health